{"tid":2182991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）又一單校園欺凌事件 受害者的自言","createTime":"2020-08-31T15:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T04:42:27.000Z","uid":373338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6858ee47c29332cca91e14a1db1c47595f782057","tid":2182991,"uid":373338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"依幾日突然見到一個廣告，見到下面呢個<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 唐家麟 </span></span>可以做到所謂KOL/FamJ，果下真係好燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學嘅時候參與一次又一次既集體欺凌，點解依啲人無報應，點解往往都係依啲仆街可以活得好好，而被佢或者佢班朋友當課餘玩意既人，就永遠需要活係痛苦之中。<br />\n<br />\n一諗返中學生活，就只係一幕幕比人取笑，作為過街老鼠一樣嘅片段。<br />\n<br />\n佢地作為欺凌者，從來都無考慮過會造成人地咁多年嘅影響，永遠都唔清楚被欺凌嘅，私下想尋死幾多次。<br />\n<br />\n依啲人點解重無有天收，重可以日日收錢影相，食好住好，好似以往所有嘢都唔關佢事唔存在一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mfv8yDN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfv8yDN.png&h=9c9d9c24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"805ffb5e437ae23cbf3afc7f0c36afc8cfa27153","tid":2182991,"uid":85403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"想知多啲，推！"},{"pid":"bd6d6258c2fa08a4ed3673d85475e84d4def39ca","tid":2182991,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"推，欺凌樓主？"},{"pid":"95ade5a438e7384c8b34099529cc512c4505ead2","tid":2182991,"uid":373338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd6d6258c2fa08a4ed3673d85475e84d4def39ca","tid":2182991,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"推，欺凌樓主？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"當年有份被欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"